room_title: Escape room "Assassination Express" by Escapology Cincinnati in Cincinnati
room_description:
You will travel back in time to 1932 Minnesota aboard a train carrying the future President of the United States, Franklin D. Roosevelt. In the new timeline that was just illegally created, a bomb has killed Franklin D Roosevelt while campaigning in Minnesota by train.
Franklin D. Roosevelt never became President of the United States, never implemented his New Deal Policy that helped the country prosper, and the United States, broke and demoralized, never entered World War II leaving Europe open to Nazi domination. You will be transported to the dining cart of the train just before bomb detonation to defuse the bomb.
